about.title: CRAFTING DIGITAL EXPERIENCES WITH MERN STACK EXPERTISE
about.description: As a dedicated Full Stack Developer with extensive experience in the MERN stack, I bring a comprehensive approach to web and mobile app development. Let's work together to bring your vision to life.
